{"tid":2052026,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"耿爽離任外交部發言人，臨別感言：我們後會有期","createTime":"2020-06-05T08:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T11:58:27.000Z","uid":58841,"like":119,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"b05fb4abc887fca1a16c325d741317833b1a112c","tid":2052026,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"6月5日的外交部例行記者會上，發言人耿爽宣布，他將不再擔任外交部新聞司副司長、發言人。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽說：&ldquo;由於工作安排的原因，我即將奔赴新的崗位，今天應該是我作為外交部發言人最後一次主持例行記者會，藉此機會我對大家在過去近4年時間裡給予我的關心、幫助、支持、鼓勵表示衷心感謝，作為一名中國外交官，無論走到哪裡，我都會繼續講好中國故事，傳遞中國聲音，為促進中國與世界的相互了解、增進中國人民與世界人民的友好情誼作出自己的努力與貢獻，在此跟大家道邊，我們後會有期。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202006/05/WS5ed9f8f9e4b00aba04d20259.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bjd.com.cn%2Fa%2F202006%2F05%2FWS5ed9f8f9e4b00aba04d20259.html&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGeIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=362fbb0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202006/05/WS5ed9f8f9e4b00aba04d20259.html</a>"},{"pid":"96be70a5817e6eb69ab37f5a4d8f12c1c93e0011","tid":2052026,"uid":266342,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:06:44.000Z","msg":"堅夫瑩婦以後冇得爽歪歪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5377529468d180664c27c51f062cc5b9ab91ad4d","tid":2052026,"uid":209278,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:06:49.000Z","msg":"所以 爽死了？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed333746cfa19271e76c66d1c2e4dc276c4ebd9c","tid":2052026,"uid":58841,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:07:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>爽死了</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\